---
title: Cherry-Glazed Beef & Pearl Couscous with Veggies & Almonds
description: We’re ready to pitch a dinner that will knock your socks off. Starting off, there’s a cherry glaze, the real hero of the story that makes us fall madly in love with seared beef rump. Let’s not forget the standout duo of pearl couscous and roast veggies, everyone knows them. It’s a five-star rating dinner that everybody will be hooked on. It's like Christmas came early!

